gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.common
Class FunctionManager

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.common.FunctionManager

public class FunctionManager
extends java.lang.Object

This is the controller class of Middle Panel JGraph implementation.

The MiddlePanelJGraphController class will deal with real implementation of some of actions to modify (mainly CRUD) upon graph, and mainly focuses on drag-and-drop and handlings of repaint of graph, for example. MiddlePanelMarqueeHandler will help handle key and mouse driven events such as display pop menus, etc.

Since:
CMTS v1.0
